Version 4.0.0 - 11-19-2014
- Updated major version of CompassAE Platform release
- Updated party model to allow parties to have multiple users
- Updated validation messages on user to not include attirbute name
- Updated activation needed email template to support CRM user creation
- Added configuration for file url protocol
Version 3.1.8 - 08-29-2013
- Bugfix in HasSecurityRoles#roles_not
Version 3.1.7 - 08-02-2013
